description._content: TITLE May Day Festival in Keene, New Hampshire CREATOR French, J.A., Keene NH SUBJECT Festive decorations - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Stereograph of decorations for May Day 1867 in City Hall in Keene NH. This is City Hall prior to the addition of the stage and gallery. The Festival was put on by the Unitarian Society.
